# Keep build context small + never leak secrets / dev artefacts into images.
.git
.github
.gitignore
.emergent
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/build
**/dist
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/venv
**/.venv
**/.env
**/.env.*
!deploy/.env.example
**/*.log
test_reports
tests
memory
*.md
!README.md
!deploy/README.md
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
